<template>
  <n-space>
    <n-button @click="handleButtonClick">
      使用渲染函数
    </n-button>
  </n-space>
</template>

<script>
import { defineComponent } from "vue";
import { useDialog } from "naive-ui";

export default defineComponent({
  setup() {
    const dialog = useDialog();
    return {
      handleButtonClick() {
        dialog.warning({
          title: "使用渲染函数",
          content: () => "Content",
          action: () => "Action"
        });
      }
    };
  }
});
</script>
